// C documentation
//
//	/*
//	** Transfer error message text from an sqlite3_vtab.zErrMsg (text stored
//	** in memory obtained from sqlite3_malloc) into a Vdbe.zErrMsg (text stored
//	** in memory obtained from sqlite3DbMalloc).
